<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.5.10">
<l>ceṟṟavaṉ teṉṉilaṅ kaimalaṅkat tēvarpi rāṉtiru māmakaḷaip</l>
<l>peṟṟumeṉ neñcakaṅ kōyilkoṇṭa pēraru ḷāḷaṉpe rumaipēcak</l>
<l>kaṟṟavaṉ kāmaru cīrkkaliyaṉ kaṇṇakat tummaṉat tumakalāk</l>
<l>koṟṟavaṉ muṟṟula kāḷiniṉṟa kuṟuṅkuṭik kēyeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Make sure you take me to Kuṟuṅkuṭi where stands</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who rules the whole earth,</l>
<l>The victor who does not leave from the mind and eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">of Kaliyaṉ of desired esteem,</l>
<l>[Of] him who learned to speak of the greatness of the one who raged</l>
<l rend="indent">to trouble Laṅkā of the South, the lord of the gods,</l>
<l>The bestower of great grace who took as [his] temple my inner heart</l>
<l rend="indent">even though having gotten the great lady Tiru.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
